<section class="topArea signUp_topArea">
    <img src="img/topArea/Hero-Desktop_Penguin.webp">
    <div class="inner_topArea w1510">
        <h2>회원가입<span>Sign Up</span></h2>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="topArea_tit">
    <div class="w1510">
        <div class="topArea_txt">
            <h3>회원정보 입력</h3>
            <p>펭귄클래식코리아에 가입할 정보를 입력해주세요.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<article class="signUp">
    <div class="signUp_wrap w1280">
        <form class="signUpForm" method="post" action="">
            <table class="signUpTable">
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="name" class="sp_title">이름</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" name="name" id="sp_name" class="sp_input" placeholder="이름을 입력해주세요."></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="id" class="sp_title">아이디</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" name="id" id="sp_id" class="sp_input" placeholder="아이디를 입력해주세요."></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="pwd" class="sp_title">비밀번호</label></td>
                    <td><input type="password" name="pwd" id="sp_pwd" class="sp_input" placeholder="(대/소문자,숫자,특수문자 3종 포함 8~15자리 미만)"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="email" class="sp_title">이메일</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" name="email" id="sp_email" class="sp_input" placeholder="(예: penguin11@gmail.com)"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="p_num" class="sp_title">전화번호</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" name="p_num" id="sp_p_num" class="sp_input" placeholder="(예: 01012341234)"></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="signUpBtn_wrap w1280">
                <td colspan="2"><input type="submit" value="회원가입" class="btnClick"></td>
                <td colspan="2"><input type="button" value="취소" class="btnBack" onclick="location.href='/'"></td>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</article>